:01.000Z","msg":"由心出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993ffd2642fc98fc333f10dc456c136b54b8aa62","tid":2080471,"uid":271959,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"最近都諗緊呢個問題<br />\n上網睇到一個theory叫attachment theory<br />\n如果細細個屋企人俾到安全感你,你大個左就有多d安全感同信任<br />\n不過我諗信任好多時係自己俾自己<br />\n你可以揀信一個人<br />\n但揀左就唔好咁容易去質疑<br />\n用人不疑 疑人不用<br />\n但點樣揀信咩人同埋點樣去學信任就好值得深究"},{"pid":"82b826300d751a504bb3c3374eedf303a3928975","tid":2080471,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cfc3e01aeb613654422069256c2d59a6cdfee2a","tid":2080471,"uid":2342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"每人既attachment style唔同<br />\n唔夾咪無信任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"逃避型都逃避型有乜信任可言 只係杜絕信任嘅可能性"},{"pid":"73f4f15e907f442ece9abaf3939e7b1ad1fd1a69","tid":2080471,"uid":336090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"993ffd2642fc98fc333f10dc456c136b54b8aa62","tid":2080471,"uid":271959,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"最近都諗緊呢個問題<br />\n上網睇到一個theory叫attachment theory<br />\n如果細細個屋企人俾到安全感你,你大個左就有多d安全感同信任<br />\n不過我諗信任好多時係自己俾自己<br />\n你可以揀信一個人<br />\n但揀左就唔好咁容易去質疑<br />\n用人不疑 疑人不用<br />\n但點樣揀信咩人同埋點樣去學信任就好值得深究"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你想知道多啲<br />\n我建議你去睇下篇文<br />\nThe role of attachment security in adolescent and adult close relationship<br />\n入面有詳細講到各種依戀係點產生<br />\n仲有解決方法<br />\n<br />\n不過都幾長，好似有成50頁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf21c6c7283072ed4efaefcdf2f5f4b7b3e3774","tid":2080471,"uid":2342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"82b826300d751a504bb3c3374eedf303a3928975","tid":2080471,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cfc3e01